{"id":165001,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2011/07/肖雪慧-九十了，到处都给染红了/","date":"2011-07-01T19:30:29Z","modified":"2011-07-01T19:30:29Z","title":"肖雪慧 | 九十了，到处都给染红了","content":"<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://photo.blog.sina.com.cn/showpic.html#blogid=5a0f796501017ow9&#038;url=http://s1.sinaimg.cn/orignal/5a0f79654a6f8862b7d50\"></a></p>\n<p><strong>山河一片红</strong>：</p>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://photo.blog.sina.com.cn/showpic.html#blogid=5a0f796501017ow9&#038;url=http://s9.sinaimg.cn/orignal/5a0f79654a6f88631b448\"><img height=\"354\" src=\"http://s9.sinaimg.cn/middle/5a0f79654a6f88631b448&#038;690\" width=\"500\" name=\"image_operate_39351309488133328\" alt=\"九十了，到处都给染红了\" title=\"九十了，到处都给染红了\" /></a></p>\n<p>被簇拥在红衣红孩红背景之中</p>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://photo.blog.sina.com.cn/showpic.html#blogid=5a0f796501017ow9&#038;url=http://s16.sinaimg.cn/orignal/5a0f79654a6f88fe1646f\"><img height=\"359\" src=\"http://simg.sinajs.cn/blog7style/images/common/sg_trans.gif\" width=\"490\" name=\"image_operate_95031309487189093\" alt=\"九十了，到处都给染红了\" title=\"九十了，到处都给染红了\" /></a></p>\n<p>红卫视</p>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://photo.blog.sina.com.cn/showpic.html#blogid=5a0f796501017ow9&#038;url=http://s6.sinaimg.cn/orignal/5a0f79654a6f886867375\"><img height=\"365\" src=\"http://simg.sinajs.cn/blog7style/images/common/sg_trans.gif\" width=\"550\" name=\"image_operate_6111309487191546\" alt=\"九十了，到处都给染红了\" title=\"九十了，到处都给染红了\" /></a><br />红短信</p>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://photo.blog.sina.com.cn/showpic.html#blogid=5a0f796501017ow9&#038;url=http://s9.sinaimg.cn/orignal/5a0f79654a6f886dcdf68\"><img src=\"http://simg.sinajs.cn/blog7style/images/common/sg_trans.gif\" name=\"image_operate_35461309487202546\" alt=\"九十了，到处都给染红了\" title=\"九十了，到处都给染红了\" /></a><br />红微博</p>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://photo.blog.sina.com.cn/showpic.html#blogid=5a0f796501017ow9&#038;url=http://s5.sinaimg.cn/orignal/5a0f79654a6f886a2ee04\"><img height=\"600\" src=\"http://simg.sinajs.cn/blog7style/images/common/sg_trans.gif\" width=\"285\" name=\"image_operate_47761309487215218\" alt=\"九十了，到处都给染红了\" title=\"九十了，到处都给染红了\" /></a></p>\n<p>红交警</p>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://photo.blog.sina.com.cn/showpic.html#blogid=5a0f796501017ow9&#038;url=http://s2.sinaimg.cn/orignal/5a0f79654a6f8869cacf1\"><img height=\"362\" src=\"http://simg.sinajs.cn/blog7style/images/common/sg_trans.gif\" width=\"490\" name=\"image_operate_87111309487216468\" alt=\"九十了，到处都给染红了\" title=\"九十了，到处都给染红了\" /></a></p>\n<p>红孩子</p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://photo.blog.sina.com.cn/showpic.html#blogid=5a0f796501017ow9&#038;url=http://s10.sinaimg.cn/orignal/5a0f79654a6f89a41a679\"><img height=\"263\" src=\"http://simg.sinajs.cn/blog7style/images/common/sg_trans.gif\" width=\"440\" name=\"image_operate_51911309488176375\" alt=\"九十了，到处都给染红了\" title=\"九十了，到处都给染红了\" /></a><br />红脸蛋——千万别说脸泛红晕是女子专利！</p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://photo.blog.sina.com.cn/showpic.html#blogid=5a0f796501017ow9&#038;url=http://s16.sinaimg.cn/orignal/5a0f79654a6f886ca3daf\"><img src=\"http://simg.sinajs.cn/blog7style/images/common/sg_trans.gif\" name=\"image_operate_52871309488165312\" alt=\"九十了，到处都给染红了\" title=\"九十了，到处都给染红了\" /></a></p>\n<p>山河泛红，树也红</p>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://photo.blog.sina.com.cn/showpic.html#blogid=5a0f796501017ow9&#038;url=http://s5.sinaimg.cn/orignal/5a0f79654a6f886d78f84\"><img height=\"340\" src=\"http://simg.sinajs.cn/blog7style/images/common/sg_trans.gif\" width=\"500\" name=\"image_operate_45061309488239296\" alt=\"九十了，到处都给染红了\" title=\"九十了，到处都给染红了\" /></a></p>\n<p>走红路——只要不影响上班时间，不花纳税人钱，谁愿走，走吧！</p>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://photo.blog.sina.com.cn/showpic.html#blogid=5a0f796501017ow9&#038;url=http://s5.sinaimg.cn/orignal/5a0f79654a6f8b5a54f24\"><img height=\"180\" src=\"http://simg.sinajs.cn/blog7style/images/common/sg_trans.gif\" width=\"240\" name=\"image_operate_34881309488180078\" alt=\"九十了，到处都给染红了\" title=\"九十了，到处都给染红了\" /></a><br />这个姿势很眼熟</p>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://photo.blog.sina.com.cn/showpic.html#blogid=5a0f796501017ow9&#038;url=http://s8.sinaimg.cn/orignal/5a0f79654a6f8866fc4e7\"><img height=\"348\" src=\"http://simg.sinajs.cn/blog7style/images/common/sg_trans.gif\" width=\"500\" name=\"image_operate_61501309488242656\" alt=\"九十了，到处都给染红了\" title=\"九十了，到处都给染红了\" /></a></p>\n<p>台上红</p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://photo.blog.sina.com.cn/showpic.html#blogid=5a0f796501017ow9&#038;url=http://s4.sinaimg.cn/orignal/5a0f79654a6f8a06bbee3\"><img height=\"365\" src=\"http://simg.sinajs.cn/blog7style/images/common/sg_trans.gif\" width=\"540\" name=\"image_operate_80621309486969765\" alt=\"九十了，到处都给染红了\" title=\"九十了，到处都给染红了\" /></a></p>\n<p>台下红</p>\n<p><b>红歌唱响，神迹频现：</b></p>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://photo.blog.sina.com.cn/showpic.html#blogid=5a0f796501017ow9&#038;url=http://s10.sinaimg.cn/orignal/5a0f79654a6f8a0007719\"><img src=\"http://simg.sinajs.cn/blog7style/images/common/sg_trans.gif\" name=\"image_operate_13581309488251640\" alt=\"九十了，到处都给染红了\" title=\"九十了，到处都给染红了\" /></a></p>\n<p>“聋哑学校红歌嘹亮”：党行神迹，铁树开花——失聪聋人不跑调，哑人能发声。日前还有报道消息说红歌唱醒植物人、治疗癌症</p>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://photo.blog.sina.com.cn/showpic.html#blogid=5a0f796501017ow9&#038;url=http://s5.sinaimg.cn/orignal/5a0f79654a6f8a08aa8a4\"><img height=\"354\" src=\"http://simg.sinajs.cn/blog7style/images/common/sg_trans.gif\" width=\"531\" name=\"image_operate_82531309488100062\" alt=\"九十了，到处都给染红了\" title=\"九十了，到处都给染红了\" /></a></p>\n<p>\n红歌红诗出成绩——近年中国女排在国际比赛成绩极度不佳，自4月26日至5月1日为期一周时间，女排在漳州训练馆和公寓的会议室学习、朗诵毛泽东诗词。教练表示，背完毛诗能让人“浑身是劲”，征战奥运必有佳绩。</p>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://photo.blog.sina.com.cn/showpic.html#blogid=5a0f796501017ow9&#038;url=http://s4.sinaimg.cn/orignal/5a0f79654a6f8a0cef073\"><img height=\"330\" src=\"http://simg.sinajs.cn/blog7style/images/common/sg_trans.gif\" width=\"440\" name=\"image_operate_79761309488099765\" alt=\"九十了，到处都给染红了\" title=\"九十了，到处都给染红了\" /></a></p>\n<p>四川佛教、道教、伊斯兰教、天主教、基督教大师五教合一集体唱红。</p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://photo.blog.sina.com.cn/showpic.html#blogid=5a0f796501017ow9&#038;url=http://s5.sinaimg.cn/orignal/5a0f79654a6f8a0d65864\"><img height=\"294\" src=\"http://simg.sinajs.cn/blog7style/images/common/sg_trans.gif\" width=\"440\" name=\"image_operate_14391309488099328\" alt=\"九十了，到处都给染红了\" title=\"九十了，到处都给染红了\" /></a></p>\n<p>唱红延年益寿</p>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://photo.blog.sina.com.cn/showpic.html#blogid=5a0f796501017ow9&#038;url=http://s9.sinaimg.cn/orignal/5a0f79654a6f8a051a328\"><img height=\"498\" src=\"http://simg.sinajs.cn/blog7style/images/common/sg_trans.gif\" width=\"690\" name=\"image_operate_47921309487708578\" alt=\"九十了，到处都给染红了\" title=\"九十了，到处都给染红了\" /></a><br />这个不太争气——6月28日下午，第二届全国红色运动会比赛项目“巧儿担架队”，庆阳市镇原县代表队1146号运动员曲军霞饰演抬担架中的“巧儿”，抬着“伤员”在沿赛道越过10米长的低网后，抬头时不幸撞上低网上的铁杆，头部受伤流血。多位女运动员因为疼痛而落泪。</p>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://photo.blog.sina.com.cn/showpic.html#blogid=5a0f796501017ow9&#038;url=http://s11.sinaimg.cn/orignal/5a0f79654a6f8a0b9764a\"><img height=\"444\" src=\"http://simg.sinajs.cn/blog7style/images/common/sg_trans.gif\" width=\"690\" name=\"image_operate_13891309488097765\" alt=\"九十了，到处都给染红了\" title=\"九十了，到处都给染红了\" /></a></p>\n<p>被撞伤了</p>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://photo.blog.sina.com.cn/showpic.html#blogid=5a0f796501017ow9&#038;url=http://s12.sinaimg.cn/orignal/5a0f79654a6f89fdbe4cb\"><img height=\"308\" src=\"http://simg.sinajs.cn/blog7style/images/common/sg_trans.gif\" width=\"440\" name=\"image_operate_93581309487727453\" alt=\"九十了，到处都给染红了\" title=\"九十了，到处都给染红了\" /></a></p>\n<p>\n地现党徽石头，就等天降祥瑞了：据华西都市报，四川宜宾惊现“党徽奇石”。圆形铁胆石上一把镰刀和一只铁锤交叉的图案，状如党徽。收藏者苏中祥说：“这是5年前我偶然在一个农民手里看见的，当即借钱买了下来。我要好好爱护，在党100周岁生日的时候把它献给党！”啊，100岁还来一次一片红！ </p>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://photo.blog.sina.com.cn/showpic.html#blogid=5a0f796501017ow9&#038;url=http://s9.sinaimg.cn/orignal/5a0f79654a6f89fd0efb8\"><img height=\"317\" src=\"http://simg.sinajs.cn/blog7style/images/common/sg_trans.gif\" width=\"490\" name=\"image_operate_78001309488091781\" alt=\"九十了，到处都给染红了\" title=\"九十了，到处都给染红了\" /></a></p>\n<p><span><br />\n红歌调节精神病人情绪——《资阳日报》等报道称，四川资阳等地的精神病医院依靠唱红歌等方法调节病人情绪，有的还举办红歌比赛，比赛的图片刊登在资阳日报上后广泛流传</span></p>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://photo.blog.sina.com.cn/showpic.html#blogid=5a0f796501017ow9&#038;url=http://s13.sinaimg.cn/orignal/5a0f79654a6f8ad0e9f0c\"><img height=\"180\" src=\"http://simg.sinajs.cn/blog7style/images/common/sg_trans.gif\" width=\"240\" name=\"image_operate_77821309487967312\" alt=\"九十了，到处都给染红了\" title=\"九十了，到处都给染红了\" /></a></p>\n<p>重庆红歌唱进了监狱，市司法局领导前往视察，还没进门，就听见犯人齐唱“我们是共产主义接班人”&#8230;&#8230;<br />\n哈，共产主义接班人在这里。</p>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://photo.blog.sina.com.cn/showpic.html#blogid=5a0f796501017ow9&#038;url=http://s12.sinaimg.cn/orignal/5a0f79654a6f8ae7c4c2b\"><img src=\"http://simg.sinajs.cn/blog7style/images/common/sg_trans.gif\" name=\"image_operate_80121309488090718\" alt=\"九十了，到处都给染红了\" title=\"九十了，到处都给染红了\" /></a><br />安徽监狱红歌会</p>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://photo.blog.sina.com.cn/showpic.html#blogid=5a0f796501017ow9&#038;url=http://s9.sinaimg.cn/orignal/5a0f796507718de98d118\"></a> </p>\n<p><em>This entry passed through the <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://fivefilters.org/content-only/\">Full-Text RSS</a> service — if this is your content and you&#39;re reading it on someone else&#39;s site, please read the FAQ at <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://fivefilters.org/content-only/faq.php#publishers\">fivefilters.org/content-only/faq.php#publishers</a>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://fivefilters.org\">Five Filters</a> featured article: <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://medialens.org/index.php?option=com_content&#038;view=article&#038;id=626\">Ten Years Of Media Lens &#8211; Our Problem With Mainstream Dissidents</a>.</em></p>\n</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2011/07/50